@DATABASE "Masters Of The Universe"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - M - Masters Of The Universe"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - M
                   ====================================

                          Masters Of The Universe
                          =======================



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(42173,0)"}          42173,0
@{"Immunity      " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(51406,0)"}          51406,0
@{"Slows Clock   " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(52346,60)"}          52346,60
@{"One Ghost     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(43210,1)"}          43210,1
@{"No Chords     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(41420,175) ZXAMPoke(41421,0)"}          41420,175:41421.0
@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(41274,255)"}          41274,255


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is for the MOVIE version by Gremlin.

                         Rastan.
@endnode
